snippet.title: King Kong for the Atari 2600
snippet.description:
Nice game...

I don't know if it's based off the movie or not (yes, it has the same name, but back then nobody gave a damn about licenses), but if it is, then it is one of the better movie games I've played.

The later levels get ridiculously fast though.
